@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_egfmij(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v0
    tmp = 0.36
    v2 = 0.19
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = (wp.cos(v0) / ((v0 + 0.55 * tmp + 0.50) - wp.cos(v2 + 0.62)))
    v0 = wp.sin((0.68 - wp.abs(tmp + 0.29)))
    data[tid] = v0
